snippet.title: Big Debate on Pathankot Attack: Is Congress trying to do politics?

localized.description:
Big Debate on Pathankot Attack: Is Congress trying to do politics?

The debate is being moderated by Neha Pant. It has the following panelists:

1. Sambit Patra (BJP)
2. Rita Bahuguna (Congress)
3. Naved Siddiqui (SP)
4. Kanchan Gupta (Senior Journalist)

For latest breaking news, other top stories log on to:  http://www.abplive.in & http://www.youtube.com/abpnewsTV
